<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,1350,1917]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1350,1375]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">Description.</emphasis>
Body (
<figureCitation box="[383,453,1350,1374]" captionStart="FIGURE 2. a – d" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1574,1597]" captionTargetBox="[185,1407,567,1535]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[172,1415,555,1552]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 2. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida) furcata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida? imminuta Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida? megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – p. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222872/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[437,453,1350,1374]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="2.0">
<date box="[437,453,1350,1374]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">2</date>
</number>
</figureCitation>
i, j) light yellowish. Coronal suture (
<figureCitation box="[871,940,1350,1374]" captionStart="FIGURE 2. a – d" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1574,1597]" captionTargetBox="[185,1407,567,1535]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[172,1415,555,1552]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 2. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida) furcata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida? imminuta Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida? megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – p. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222872/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[926,940,1350,1374]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="2.0">2</number>
</figureCitation>
k) only visible in basal half of vertex. Face (
<figureCitation box="[159,227,1386,1410]" captionStart="FIGURE 2. a – d" captionStartId="8.[151,250,1574,1597]" captionTargetBox="[185,1407,567,1535]" captionTargetId="figure@8.[172,1415,555,1552]" captionTargetPageId="8" captionText="FIGURE 2. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida) furcata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida? imminuta Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida? megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – p. Kapsa (Rigida) serrata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222872/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[212,227,1386,1410]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="2.0">2</number>
</figureCitation>
l) long.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,1350,1917]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Abdominal apodemes (
<figureCitation box="[460,540,1425,1449]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[512,540,1425,1449]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
a) broad, not exceeding the hind margin of the 
<number box="[1068,1082,1425,1449]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="3.0">3</number>
rd sternite. Anal tube appendage (
<figureCitation box="[159,239,1461,1485]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[212,239,1461,1485]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
b–d) broad, apical hook short.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,1350,1917]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Pygofer dorsal appendage (
<figureCitation box="[507,587,1497,1521]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[560,587,1497,1521]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
b–d) tapering towards apex and curved ventrad. Subgenital plate (
<figureCitation box="[1334,1416,1497,1521]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[1387,1416,1497,1521]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
b, f) with 
<number box="[242,256,1533,1557]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="4.0">4</number>
macrosetae, central area of lateral margin without microsetae. Paramere (
<figureCitation box="[1121,1206,1533,1557]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[1178,1206,1533,1557]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="1.2" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" unit="g" value="12.0">12</quantity>
</figureCitation>
g) with apical tooth slender and long, slightly curved dorsad. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[766,847,1569,1593]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[819,847,1569,1593]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="12.0">12</number>
</figureCitation>
h) with lateral arms and manubrium long. Aedeagal shaft (
<figureCitation box="[224,310,1605,1629]" captionStart="FIGURE 12" captionStartId="19.[151,250,1052,1075]" captionTargetBox="[181,1405,206,1026]" captionTargetId="figure@19.[166,1420,193,1031]" captionTargetPageId="19" captionText="FIGURE 12. Kapsa (Rigida) megaprocessa Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. abdominal apodemes; b. genital capsule; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; d. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; e. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; f. subgenital plate, dorsal view; g. paramere, dorsal view; h. connective; i. aedeagus, lateral view; j. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222882/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
Fig. 
<number box="[280,310,1605,1629]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="12.0">
<date box="[280,310,1605,1629]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135" value="2012-01">12</date>
</number>
</figureCitation>
i, j) slim, denticulate dorsoapically, ventral process broadened in side view; dorsal apodeme well developed, preatrium large, slightly shorter than aedeagal shaft; gonopore apical, ventral.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1436,1350,1917]" box="[199,737,1677,1701]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,371,1677,1701]" pageId="18" pageNumber="135">Measurement.</emphasis>
